OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTriple lock for pensions to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstay if Tories win election
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Jeremy Hunt has said the Conservatives 
OL,6, will keep the triple lock system to    
OL,7, decide rises in the state pension if   
OL,8, they win the election.                 
OL,10,FThe chancellor confirmed the pledge,   
OL,11,Fwhich means the pension rises in line  
OL,12,Fwith average earnings growth, inflation
OL,13,For 2.5% - whichever is highest.        
OL,15,FHe told Sunday with Laura Kuenssberg he
OL,16,Fwas confident the "expensive" promise  
OL,17,Fwould be paid by growing the economy.  
OL,19,FLabour said it was "committed to       
OL,20,Fretaining" the triple lock.            
